    <date day="11" month="March" year="2017"/>
    <abstract>
      <t>This specification defines a new extension, LMA-Controlled-MAG-
   Session-Params to Proxy Mobile IPv6.  This option can be used by the
   local mobility anchor in Proxy Mobile IPv6 signaling for notifying
   the mobile access gateway to conform to various parameters contained
   in this extension.</t>
    </abstract>
